wiring the two running lights together then attached the turn signals and 
brake lights.  Now my problem is when I step on the brakes, my brake lights 
are now my flashers (orange lights).  How does one separate the turn 
signal/brake light wire?  Is this physically possible without running a new 
wire from somewhere?  Somebody must have performed this operation!
